{"tid":2077944,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"康城Sea to Sky收過萬票 超額21倍","createTime":"2020-06-24T16:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T02:51:01.000Z","uid":199670,"like":18,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2067d51d14c77e260e02c56c03be34afa0373280","tid":2077944,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"新盤市場氣氛熾熱，長實旗下日出康城8期SEA TO SKY將於本周六推售462伙。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，截至下午10時，<span style=\"color: red;\">項目累收約10,483票，破天荒超額認購逾21倍</span>，將於本周五（26日）下午3時截票，料可超越新地（0016）Wetland Seasons Park收逾萬票的成績，料成今年新盤票王。<br />\n<br />\n長實執行董事趙國雄早前表示，項目收票情況理想，認為港版國安法令本港經濟前景更明朗、更有信心，而市民買樓熱烈，亦反映對國安法感到安心，料下半年樓價可達5至7%升幅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 一人4票水票都2千幾票 仲要只係其中一個盤。 經濟差？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港大把有錢人</span>"},{"pid":"7bc5fe250af403d5a73a7caa2fdd18ead55c21f8","tid":2077944,"uid":199670,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"明明連燈仔話置安法樓價會大跌9成 冇人要<br />\n我仲要等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4628f9e8b36669feb67bb22cec668338949155","tid":2077944,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc5fe250af403d5a73a7caa2fdd18ead55c21f8","tid":2077944,"uid":199670,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"明明連燈仔話置安法樓價會大跌9成 冇人要<br />\n我仲要等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"國安法*"},{"pid":"c2995305c50257c2c004ec85cd52baf46f8ec0c6","tid":2077944,"ui